        <id>https://qinguoxiaozi.github.io/post/cang-hai-yi-sheng-xiao/</id>
        <link href="https://qinguoxiaozi.github.io/post/cang-hai-yi-sheng-xiao/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-03-24T06:42:36.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>笑傲江湖<br>
-瀚海孤客<br>
弦化沧海一声笑，浪滔波怒万里鸣。<br>
寒光浮影水中现，白马银鞍飒踏星。<br>
江山多娇怜人醉，佳人才子定终情。<br>
万丈豪情凌云冲，平生襟抱胸中醒。</p>
]]></content>
